&lt;p&gt;Timescale powers the next wave of computing, and we are enabling our customers to build innovative, data-centric applications powered by Timescale. As an&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Account Executive, &lt;/strong&gt;you will interact directly with customers, answer questions, provide information, and build connections with them.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be at the forefront of closing deals and providing solutions in our growing database market. You can make a meaningful impact by helping organizations harness the power of data for better decision-making, improved operations, and innovation. You will manage complex sales relationships with critical customers and effectively communicate the value of Timescale. As the company and industry expand, we see our high-growth market as an opportunity for significant sales and career advancement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your main responsibilities will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on closing Sales Qualified Leads (SQL) from the marketing team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify leads based on their challenges and alignment with our product suite.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategically prospect into CTOs, Engineering Leads, and Technical End Users.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full sales cycle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage resources such as Sales Engineers and Data Architects effectively.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide relevant stakeholders through the sales process to close.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A little bit about you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a top performer with a proven track record, and you know that your success directly depends on your customers&#39; success. You always put the customer&#39;s best interests first while managing complex sales engagements and effectively leveraging resources to ensure success. You are hungry, resilient, curious, driven, and humble in your pursuit of excellence. You aren‚Äôt afraid to speak up and identify problem areas or share your ideas, and you want to be a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;part of the solution&lt;/strong&gt;! You are a builder who is passionate about creatively trying new things and contributing to our growth by exploring innovative solutions üôå.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You also have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;3-5 years of experience in a full-cycle quota-carrying Saas sales role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Technical background with a deep understanding of database technology, data platforms, open source, and cloud ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Ability to articulate the business value of complex enterprise technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proficiency in modern sales software (e.g., Salesforce, Outreach, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven track record of exceeding sales targets and driving revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strong interpersonal skills with the ability to build rapport and establish trust with customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with a proactive approach to problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About TimescaleüêØ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Timescale is the creator of TimescaleDB, the industry-leading relational database for time-series. Tens of thousands of organizations trust TimescaleDB today with their mission-critical time-series applications. The company is dedicated to serving software developers and businesses worldwide, enabling them to build exceptional data-driven products that &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;measure everything that matters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;: software applications, industrial equipment, financial markets, blockchain activity, consumer behavior, machine learning models, climate change, and more. Analyzing data across the time dimension (‚Äútime-series data‚Äù) enables developers to understand what is happening right now, how that is changing, and why that is changing. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Timescale is a remote-first company with a globalüåé workforce and is backed by Tiger Global, Benchmark Capital, New Enterprise Associates, Redpoint Ventures, Icon Ventures, Two Sigma Ventures, and other leading investors. For more information, visit www.timescale.com or follow @TimescaleDB.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working at TimescaleüêØ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Timescale is breaking boundaries and setting new standards in the innovating and rapidly growing time-series data industry. Built on the foundation of people-focused values and principles, Timescale makes sure integrity, mutual respect, and compassion is at the heart of everything we do. Empowered by our Co-Founders, Ajay Kulkarni (CEO) and Mike Freedman (CTO), we are challenging the norm by working with people who continuously inspire and teach us ü§ù.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Enjoy debating the crunch-factor of different chicken nuggets üçó, sweating it out during lunch üí¶, talking about your kids, whether they be actual children üë∂üèΩ, potted plants ü™¥, or four-legged creatures üêæ? You‚Äôll fit right in at Timescale!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we‚Äôre offering&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Flexible PTO and family leave&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Summer Fridays off in August ‚òÄÔ∏è&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Full remote work from almost &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;anywhere&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Stock options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Monthly WiFi stipend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Professional development &amp;amp; educational benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Premium insurance options for you and your family &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(US employees)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;FSA/Dependent FSA plans &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(US employees)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;401(k) retirement plan &lt;em&gt;(US employees)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;While Timescale operates primarily as a remote organization, we strongly prefer candidates located in San Francisco, CA, and New York City, NY, to facilitate frequent collaboration and connection with local team members&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;By applying for this position, you are agreeing to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.timescale.com/legal/timescale-applicant-privacy-notice&quot;&gt;Timescale&#39;s Applicant Privacy Notice.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Content Marketing Manager &lt;/strong&gt;at TimescaleüêØ, you will support lead-generation efforts by collaborating across multiple departments to repurpose content for various channels and audiences. You will work closely with the Lead Generation and Content Marketing team to implement efficient processes and provide compelling and engaging written, visual, audio, and video content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Top candidates will have a knack for transforming existing content into fresh, impactful formats, including social media posts, infographics, ad copy, and more. You will thrive in a fast-paced environment, enjoy brainstorming innovative ideas, and possess the ability to work seamlessly with content creators, designers, and other stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, your main responsibilities will be to:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transform existing blog posts, articles, and whitepapers into new formats such as long-form content, social media posts, videos, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create shorter, engaging snippets from long-form content for use on various platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with teams to align and develop content specifically designed to attract and capture leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor, analyze, and report on the performance of repurposed content to optimize lead generation efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft compelling social media posts that drive engagement and conversions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create ad copy and visuals for various digital advertising platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with content creators, designers, and other team members to ensure all repurposed content adheres to brand guidelines and quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an organized library of repurposed content assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring innovative ideas to the table for repurposing content in new and engaging ways.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiment with different content formats and platforms to reach a wider audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role is remote, and English language fluency is a requirement. Due to the team&#39;s location, the ideal candidates are located in the US, Brazil, Portugal, or Ireland.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A little bit about you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are a self-starter who finds great fulfillment in getting things done‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs creating an effective piece of content, or developing a new operational process‚Äîand seeing the impact of your work. You are not intimidated by a fast-moving and multi-tasking environment but rather revel in the opportunity to move quickly with autonomy. You believe that working as a team can improve your own output, and you are awesome but humble and folks look forward to working with you. You‚Äôre primarily a storyteller who has created content for technical audiences and has worked collaboratively with stakeholders, developers, and designers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You also:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have at least 4 years of experience working in content, lead generation, or a similar role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess strong interpersonal and communication skills (written and verbal).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Easily pick up on technical terms and concepts and know how to explain them clearly and concisely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance the needs of both the business goals and customers when creating content.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a self-starter who can manage and prioritize initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess strong problem-solving skills combined with deep empathy for all humans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are able to work independently and remotely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;By applying for this position, you are agreeing to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.timescale.com/legal/timescale-applicant-privacy-notice&quot;&gt;Timescale&#39;s Applicant Privacy Notice.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
